{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Generously grease 4 individual pudding basins (Ø 7 cm) and 4 circles of baking paper (Ø 7 cm) with butter.","Place a bowl on mixing bowl lid and weigh in pears. Remove bowl, add lemon juice and stir, then set aside."," <strong>Insert butterfly whisk<\/strong>. Place butter and sugar in mixing bowl then cream <b>30 sec\/speed 3<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula then cream again <b>30 sec\/speed 3<b>.","Add egg and golden syrup then mix <b>20 sec\/speed 3<b>. <strong>Remove butterfly whisk<\/strong>.","Add baking powder, flour and cocoa powder then mix <b>20 sec\/speed 4<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula and mix again <b>20 sec\/speed 4<b>.","Fill prepared pudding basins with mixture up to a quarter full, then divide reserved pear pieces between them. Top with remaining sponge mixture, making sure basins are no more than ¾ full. Cover tops with prepared baking paper circles, buttered side down, and push mixture down a little. Cover each basin with foil or baking paper, secure with string or an elastic band and put into Varoma dish.","Place water in mixing bowl and place covered Varoma into position. Steam puddings <b>60 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b> or until a skewer inserted in centre comes out clean.","Remove from basins and invert onto serving plates. Serve hot with custard, cream or ice cream."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["60 g butter, soft, plus extra for greasing","160 g pears (approx. 2) peeled, cored, diced (1 cm)","1 tsp lemon juice","60 g light brown sugar","1 large egg","50 g golden syrup","½ tsp baking powder","100 g self-raising flour","25 g cocoa powder","1000 g water, for steaming"]}],"id":"r94298","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-F99oEf1gJhY\/XZWfCqT98TI\/AAAAAAAAe90\/IHdJRFTEHGc3zPmDdAaHAKlu_1n962nBgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_mhaaFqOveS2BGtXO.png","title":"Steamed Chocolate and Pear Pudding","publishedAt":"2016-10-24T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"5.5 g","fat":"15.6 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"49.9 g","calories":"1513 kJ \/ 362 kcal"},"usefulItems":"individual pudding basins, baking paper, kitchen string or elastic band, skewer","basicInfo":["easy","10m","1h 10m","4 portions"]}